      "raw_text": "ID. T. Ham, Rev. E. P. Lyon and\nJ. A. Tormey will address the meet\ning of the Women's Christian Tenn\nperance union tonight at the Jeffer-\nson Street Methodist church,\nSharp avenue and Jefferson street.\n\n\nThe twenty-third annual conven-\nton began today with a large at\ntendance. At least 100 delegates\nare expected. The sessions will\ncontinue until Friday."
